So on the horizontal axis you plot sugar consumption

00:03:28.652 --> 00:03:32.780
and then on the vertical axis you plot heart disease risk

00:03:32.780 --> 00:03:35.512
or their level of heart disease.

00:03:35.512 --> 00:03:40.908
Heart disease risk, let's say at 60.

00:03:41.862 --> 00:03:44.938
And you find a plot that looks something like this.

00:03:44.938 --> 00:03:46.474
So each of these points.

00:03:46.474 --> 00:03:51.736
This is someone who consumed 200 grams of sugar per day

00:03:51.736 --> 00:03:55.997
and they're now at high heart disease risk now at age 60.

00:03:55.997 --> 00:03:58.826
But maybe this is someone who is at low heart disease risk

00:03:58.826 --> 00:04:02.237
at age 60 even though they consumed a lot of sugar everyday.

00:04:02.806 --> 00:04:06.584
And so we just keep plotting all of these points.

00:04:07.476 --> 00:04:10.077
And you say, "Well, you know what, it does look"

00:04:10.077 --> 00:04:12.374
and obviously I'm not going to all 300.

00:04:12.374 --> 00:04:14.871
You say, "Well, actually, it looks like there is

00:04:14.871 --> 00:04:17.410
"a rough correlation right over here."

00:04:17.410 --> 00:04:19.589
That if you tried to plot a line, there's

00:04:19.589 --> 00:04:22.338
definitely some outliers here, but it looks

00:04:22.338 --> 00:04:27.112
like there is a line that you could fit.

00:04:27.112 --> 00:04:30.237
And then you might say, "It looks like sugar and heart

00:04:30.237 --> 00:04:33.088
"disease risk at age 60, that they are correlated,

00:04:33.088 --> 00:04:35.066
"that they're related in this way, that they move together,

00:04:35.066 --> 00:04:36.910
"that if someone consumed a lot of sugar over

00:04:36.910 --> 00:04:39.719
"the last 30 years they seem to have a worse

00:04:39.719 --> 00:04:43.094
"heart situation and if they consumed a lot lower sugar,

00:04:43.094 --> 00:04:47.072
"they seem to have a lower or better heart situation."

00:04:47.626 --> 00:04:51.653
This often happens in medical science, when people see

00:04:51.653 --> 00:04:53.989
