00:04:53.989 --> 00:04:57.486
oh therefore consuming more sugar

00:04:57.486 --> 00:05:00.199
must drive up heart disease risk.

00:05:00.199 --> 00:05:02.455
That's very dangerous because just seeing this data

00:05:02.455 --> 00:05:06.185
