00:05:14.491 --> 00:05:18.502
there's some other underlying cause that's making it happen.

00:05:18.502 --> 00:05:19.937
Maybe they have some other deficiency

00:05:19.937 --> 00:05:21.593
that's making them crave sugar.

00:05:21.593 --> 00:05:24.416
So it's not clear which way the causality is happening.

00:05:24.416 --> 00:05:27.568
Is the sugar consumption driving the unhealthy heart

00:05:27.568 --> 00:05:29.723
or is somehow the unhealthy heart driving the sugar

00:05:29.723 --> 00:05:32.289
