00:05:36.845 --> 00:05:39.388
will have more sugar or vice versa, who knows.

00:05:39.697 --> 00:05:42.427
All this is telling you is that there is a correlation.

00:05:42.427 --> 00:05:44.082
So this right over here, you would

00:05:44.082 --> 00:05:46.131
call this an observational study.

00:05:46.131 --> 00:05:48.020
You've observed a relationship, but you

00:05:48.020 --> 00:05:50.399
really can't say what is causing what.

00:05:50.399 --> 00:05:51.807
